      "full_name": "Legmash Plant OJSC",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Legmash Plant OJSC is a Belarusian plant which produces 152-mm and 122-mm shells for cannon artillery (including howitzers D-30, D-20, Msta-B, Giatsint-B, and the self-propelled modifications thereof). The facility also manufactures 122-mm unguided rockets of the 9M22U-1 line for the 9K51 Grad MLRS multiple rocket launcher. Therefore, Legmash Plant OJSC is an entity forming part of the military and industrial complex of Belarus.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}